<i>[Weaving A Tale of Love 2]</i>

3
00:01:32,032 --> 00:01:35,908
<i>[Episode 2]</i>

4
00:01:51,663 --> 00:01:53,368
My lady,

5
00:01:53,368 --> 00:01:54,663
Is everything fine at home?

6
00:01:54,663 --> 00:01:58,383
Master stayed at the county office last night,
and everything is fine at home,

7
00:01:58,383 --> 00:02:03,463
Except that Yunu went out last night
and has not yet returned,

8
00:02:04,023 --> 00:02:06,543
My lady, Yunu is back,

9
00:02:09,503 --> 00:02:10,703
My lady, you're back,

10
00:02:10,703 --> 00:02:12,063
Where did you go?

11
00:02:12,063 --> 00:02:14,643
There was a heavy rain last night,
and I was worried about the master,

12
00:02:14,643 --> 00:02:18,383
So I went to the county office to bring the master some wine, dishes, and a change of clothes,

13
00:02:18,383 --> 00:02:21,763
The master stayed in the county office
just to get away from you,

14
00:02:21,763 --> 00:02:25,143
And yet you had the audacity to run over there,
you're so thick-skinned,

15
00:02:25,143 --> 00:02:28,663
How do you know the master is sick of me?

16
00:02:28,663 --> 00:02:32,463
If you went to deliver things,
why are you only returning now?

17
00:02:32,463 --> 00:02:37,143
Last night, there was strong wind, heavy rain,
frequent lightning, and thunder,

18
00:02:37,143 --> 00:02:41,783
It's inconvenient to travel at night,
So I stayed overnight at the county office,

19
00:02:41,783 --> 00:02:43,843
Stay overnight?

20
00:02:46,803 --> 00:02:50,543
Yunu didn't rest well last night,
and I'm tired and weary,

21
00:02:50,543 --> 00:02:55,483
Madam, if there's nothing else,
I will go to rest first,

22
00:02:55,483 --> 00:02:59,183
As a servant, how dare you speak like this
in front of your mistress?

23
00:02:59,183 --> 00:03:01,523
Do you have any discipline left?

24
00:03:10,503 --> 00:03:14,183
My lady,
why don't you grab her and ask clearly?

25
00:03:14,183 --> 00:03:16,443
I'll go to the county office to ask Cheng,

26
00:03:16,443 --> 00:03:19,523
Stop there, come back,

27
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:30,820
<i>[Pei's Mansion]</i>

28
00:03:34,703 --> 00:03:35,968
Master,

29
00:03:35,968 --> 00:03:37,203
Has my lady returned?

30
00:03:37,203 --> 00:03:39,923
My lady returned at noon,
She is currently in the main room,

31
00:03:39,923 --> 00:03:44,063
Alright, I will go to the study first
and go see the lady later,

32
00:03:44,063 --> 00:03:46,248
I have something to ask you,

33
00:03:52,063 --> 00:03:53,663
Yunu greets my master,

34
00:03:53,663 --> 00:03:55,503
What is it?

35
00:03:55,503 --> 00:03:57,243
I'm here to admit my guilt,

36
00:03:57,243 --> 00:04:00,163
Last night was filled with thunderstorms,
and I was very scaredâ€¦

37
00:04:00,163 --> 00:04:02,348
No need for further words,

38
00:04:02,348 --> 00:04:06,363
Presumably,
the lady has already learned of it from you,

39
00:04:10,363 --> 00:04:12,703
Are you telling the truth?

40
00:04:13,343 --> 00:04:15,563
If I utter even half a lie,

41
00:04:15,563 --> 00:04:18,023
may I be punished by
sending into the hell of tongue-ripping,

42
00:04:18,763 --> 00:04:21,083
I believe you,

43
00:04:25,643 --> 00:04:29,443
Why do you torment yourself
with such a harsh oath?

44
00:04:33,743 --> 00:04:35,103
What are you doing?

45
00:04:35,103 --> 00:04:38,543
Don't move, there is a smell on you,

46
00:04:40,503 --> 00:04:43,923
Where have I smelled this scent before?

47
00:04:47,463 --> 00:04:49,308
Yunu,

48
00:04:50,883 --> 00:04:52,963
The scent is from Yunu,

49
00:05:04,623 --> 00:05:06,503
Master, lucky I stopped you first,

50
00:05:06,503 --> 00:05:09,083
If you went to see the lady,
it would have been troublesome,

51
00:05:09,783 --> 00:05:12,903
I have been feeling a bit of sick lately,
and I have a blocked nose,

52
00:05:12,903 --> 00:05:14,863
I can't smell anything, please forgive me,

53
00:05:14,863 --> 00:05:16,263
What is going on with you?

54
00:05:16,263 --> 00:05:18,323
It's like growing a pig's snout for nothing,

55
00:05:18,323 --> 00:05:21,683
Xiaotan, has Shouyue returned yet?

56
00:05:21,683 --> 00:05:24,403
The master has already returned,

57
00:05:24,403 --> 00:05:26,072
Where's he?

58
00:05:27,383 --> 00:05:29,883
The master said he was a bit tired today,

59
00:05:29,883 --> 00:05:33,603
So he went to shower and change first,
then he will go to see you, my lady,

60
00:05:34,283 --> 00:05:35,963
Is the bathwater ready so quickly?

61
00:05:35,963 --> 00:05:39,643
No, I just ordered the kitchen
to prepare some hot water first,

62
00:05:39,643 --> 00:05:41,303
There's still some work to do,

63
00:05:41,303 --> 00:05:44,923
The master should be in the study now,

64
00:05:57,083 --> 00:05:58,912
What do you mean by this?

65
00:06:12,023 --> 00:06:13,584
My lady,

66
00:06:14,163 --> 00:06:19,103
Shouyue,
why did you change your clothes before shower?

67
00:06:27,383 --> 00:06:30,063
Ask him, it's all his good work,

68
00:06:30,063 --> 00:06:32,143
Reporting to my lady, it was Cheng's oversight,

69
00:06:32,143 --> 00:06:35,263
I accidentally spilled the tea on the master's clothes just now,

70
00:06:35,263 --> 00:06:37,503
The master was in the rain yesterday
and caught a cold,

71
00:06:37,503 --> 00:06:39,283
He must not catch a cold again today,

72
00:06:39,283 --> 00:06:42,583
So I helped changed clothes for the master,

73
00:06:46,243 --> 00:06:48,903
Cheng, tell me the truth,

74
00:06:48,903 --> 00:06:51,243
What exactly happened last night?

75
00:06:51,243 --> 00:06:53,663
Why does your clothing have the scent of Yunu?

76
00:06:53,663 --> 00:06:55,183
My lady, please do not get angry,

77
00:06:55,183 --> 00:06:58,523
The fragrance comes from my sachet,

78
00:07:01,843 --> 00:07:06,023
Ani, Xiaotan, you must absolutely not
speak of today's events to others,

79
00:07:06,023 --> 00:07:08,503
<i>A small gain was made from today's matter,</i>

80
00:07:08,503 --> 00:07:09,823
<i>I will lay low for a few days,</i>

81
00:07:09,823 --> 00:07:12,523
<i>then deal a heavy blow to the Kudi Clan,</i>

82
00:07:32,823 --> 00:07:35,084
<i>[Slave Purchase Deed]</i>
Madam,

83
00:07:39,183 --> 00:07:43,243
<i>[Slave Purchase Deed]</i>
The purchase deed of Yunu is here with me,

84
00:07:43,983 --> 00:07:45,443
Madam, you probably don't know yet,

85
00:07:45,443 --> 00:07:49,103
I heard that there was a huge commotion
at Pei's Mansion today,

86
00:07:49,103 --> 00:07:52,183
That Kudi Clan is after all inexperienced

87
00:07:52,183 --> 00:07:55,463
How can they withstand Madam's cunning plans?

88
00:07:55,463 --> 00:07:58,623
Go to the Pei's Mansion for me one more time,

89
00:07:58,623 --> 00:08:00,983
I have some good news,

90
00:08:00,983 --> 00:08:05,463
I need to let Pei Shouyue and Kudi Liuli know
about my means,

91
00:08:06,863 --> 00:08:10,483
Madam you are wise,
and I will take care of it right away,

92
00:08:20,103 --> 00:08:24,623
I called Lady Liuli over today
because I have something to discuss with you,

93
00:08:24,623 --> 00:08:27,343
You're so intelligent and clever,

94
00:08:27,343 --> 00:08:32,043
I'm becoming more and more interested
in your half-sister,

95
00:08:32,043 --> 00:08:35,403
Is the Princess talking about Shanhu?

96
00:08:36,723 --> 00:08:40,443
I wonder what this has to do with Shanhu,

97
00:08:41,343 --> 00:08:45,423
Cui has been helping me
look after the household chores for years,

98
00:08:45,423 --> 00:08:48,983
She was unable to bear more children
for the Crown Prince,

99
00:08:48,983 --> 00:08:53,983
I'd like to arrange a concubine
for the Crown Prince

100
00:08:53,983 --> 00:08:57,903
to extend the lineage
for Residence of the Hedong Duke,

101
00:08:57,903 --> 00:09:00,903
Yesterday, I sent someone to the Kudi's Mansion

102
00:09:00,903 --> 00:09:04,783
to propose a marriage alliance
to your half-sister, Shanhu,

103
00:09:04,783 --> 00:09:09,563
In a few days,
Shanhu will be the crown prince's,

104
00:09:12,883 --> 00:09:17,663
In a few more days,
it will be the annual Lotus Banquet,

105
00:09:17,663 --> 00:09:20,723
By that time, you and your sister

106
00:09:20,723 --> 00:09:25,503
can meet at the Lotus Banquet hosted
by my Residence of the Hedong Duke,

107
00:09:25,503 --> 00:09:27,583
Wouldn't that be fun?

108
00:09:27,583 --> 00:09:32,283
Although Shanhu is smarter than me, she is also inexperienced,

109
00:09:32,283 --> 00:09:35,823
In the future,
I hope the Princess will take good care of her,

110
00:09:35,823 --> 00:09:38,183
Why should you be modest, Lady Liuli?

111
00:09:38,183 --> 00:09:41,423
You are more beautiful and cleverer

112
00:09:41,423 --> 00:09:46,283
than my adopted daughter, Lady Luqi,

113
00:09:46,283 --> 00:09:48,703
Shouyue is a devoted lover,

114
00:09:48,703 --> 00:09:53,623
He has refused to remarry for many years
after Lady Qi's death,

115
00:09:53,623 --> 00:09:58,103
I suppose he can't forget my adopted daughter,

116
00:09:58,103 --> 00:10:02,963
Now that he has you,
and he can finally start over,

117
00:10:10,688 --> 00:10:11,872
<i>[West Market]</i>

118
00:10:16,352 --> 00:10:21,536
<i>[Kudi's Residence]</i>

119
00:10:47,503 --> 00:10:51,563
Why hasn't Shanhu come to pay her respects
to her elder sister and brother-in-law?

120
00:10:51,563 --> 00:10:53,903
Lady Shanhu said she's ill
and not fit to meet guests,

121
00:10:53,903 --> 00:10:59,056
Ill? Thisâ€¦ thisâ€¦

122
00:10:59,056 --> 00:11:01,020
Father,

123
00:11:01,020 --> 00:11:03,403
I heard Shanhu is to marry into
the Residence of the Hedong Duke,

124
00:11:03,403 --> 00:11:04,963
Shouyue and I just found out,

125
00:11:04,963 --> 00:11:08,603
so we came to discuss with you
and ask about your opinion,

126
00:11:09,283 --> 00:11:11,963
From the information I received from them,

127
00:11:12,723 --> 00:11:16,223
no lavish ceremony will be hold,

128
00:11:16,223 --> 00:11:22,743
They say the day after tomorrow,
a bridal chair will come to get your sister,

129
00:11:22,743 --> 00:11:27,123
As for the other formalities,
they will be exempted if possible,

130
00:11:30,403 --> 00:11:33,663
Today, Shouyue and Liuli are returning home,

131
00:11:33,663 --> 00:11:35,583
Listening to what was said just now,

132
00:11:35,583 --> 00:11:39,123
could it be that Shouyue has a different view
on this marriage arrangement?

133
00:11:42,983 --> 00:11:46,183
Wellâ€¦Shanhu is sick,

134
00:11:46,183 --> 00:11:49,563
Aren't you going to check on her as her mother?

135
00:11:50,243 --> 00:11:51,928
Yes,

136
00:11:53,664 --> 00:11:56,023
<i>[Overflowing Virtue]</i>

137
00:11:56,023 --> 00:11:57,343
Shouyue,

138
00:11:57,343 --> 00:12:00,523
anything improper about Shanhu marrying into
the Residence of the Hedong Duke?

139
00:12:00,523 --> 00:12:02,143
Father, there's something you don't know,

140
00:12:02,143 --> 00:12:06,023
Marriage should be about matching
in social class,

141
00:12:06,023 --> 00:12:08,383
What place is this
Residence of the Hedong Duke?

142
00:12:08,383 --> 00:12:11,703
I'm afraid we need to think it through
more carefully,

143
00:12:11,703 --> 00:12:13,823
What if Shanhu causes trouble in the future?

144
00:12:13,823 --> 00:12:15,563
What kind of power does the Princess have?

145
00:12:15,563 --> 00:12:19,263
By then, if it brings problems you,
the loss outweighs the gain,

146
00:12:20,003 --> 00:12:23,143
What should we do about this?

147
00:12:23,143 --> 00:12:25,023
Father-in-law, you are aware of this,

148
00:12:25,023 --> 00:12:28,983
There are quite a few young men
with both talent and virtue in Chang'an,

149
00:12:28,983 --> 00:12:32,303
Why does Shanhu insist on
climbing the social ladder,

150
00:12:32,303 --> 00:12:33,383
going to the Residence of the Hedong Duke

151
00:12:33,383 --> 00:12:36,123
and becoming a disreputable concubine?

152
00:12:36,123 --> 00:12:39,503
The concubines of Residence of the Hedong Duke
appear glamorous to outsiders,

153
00:12:39,503 --> 00:12:43,183
but they suffer a lot within the residence,

154
00:12:43,183 --> 00:12:44,788
Therefore,

155
00:12:45,523 --> 00:12:48,303
you should ponder it over carefully

156
00:12:48,303 --> 00:12:51,363
to truly understand the pros and cons,

157
00:12:55,563 --> 00:13:01,543
Furthermore, the Crown Prince of Hedong Duke
already has Lady Cui as his legitimate wife,

158
00:13:01,543 --> 00:13:03,863
If there's some disputes between them,

159
00:13:03,863 --> 00:13:08,763
won't she come back crying every day?

160
00:13:10,163 --> 00:13:14,323
Father-in-law, you have personally experienced
the disputes between wives and concubines,

161
00:13:14,323 --> 00:13:18,863
That incident almost led to the annihilation
of the Kudi family,

162
00:13:18,863 --> 00:13:22,923
Do you wish to go through that once more?

163
00:13:33,083 --> 00:13:34,483
I've just heard,

164
00:13:34,483 --> 00:13:36,603
Madam has sent a marriage proposal
to the Kudi family,

165
00:13:36,603 --> 00:13:40,123
wanting to take a concubine
for the Crown Prince,

166
00:13:41,123 --> 00:13:43,823
It's just thatâ€¦

167
00:13:43,823 --> 00:13:47,043
it's about the half-sister of Kudi Liuli,

168
00:13:47,043 --> 00:13:51,923
I'm rather worried,

169
00:13:52,823 --> 00:13:57,443
Although Kudi Shanhu and Kudi Liuli
were born by the same father,

170
00:13:57,443 --> 00:14:00,103
they have been discordant
since they were young,

171
00:14:00,103 --> 00:14:03,083
Speaking of which,
Ms, Cao, the mother of Shanhu,

172
00:14:03,083 --> 00:14:06,503
also aided in killing Liuli's mother,

173
00:14:06,503 --> 00:14:10,483
The two sisters are no different from enemies,

174
00:14:10,483 --> 00:14:13,703
so what is there to worry about?

175
00:14:13,703 --> 00:14:19,583
Cui, you wouldn't want to prevent the prince
from taking a concubine, would you?

176
00:14:19,583 --> 00:14:21,732
I won't dare,

177
00:14:27,183 --> 00:14:29,143
How can this be possible?

178
00:14:29,143 --> 00:14:32,703
They are just too malicious,

179
00:14:33,223 --> 00:14:36,803
Mother, don't cry, I won't let them succeed,

180
00:14:38,468 --> 00:14:38,923
<i>[Overflowing Virtue]</i>

181
00:14:38,923 --> 00:14:41,123
This matter requires careful consideration,

182
00:14:41,923 --> 00:14:44,103
You're quite the thrifty one, Pei Xingjian,

183
00:14:45,223 --> 00:14:48,143
It's all your fault,
and you have a snake's heart,

184
00:14:48,143 --> 00:14:49,280
You dare to incited Father,

185
00:14:49,280 --> 00:14:51,223
and you ruined my marriage
into the Hedong Duke's Residence,

186
00:14:51,223 --> 00:14:52,563
Wasn't Shanhu sick?

187
00:14:52,563 --> 00:14:55,703
How have you recovered in just short time?

188
00:14:55,703 --> 00:14:58,528
Our family's affair is none of your business,

189
00:14:58,528 --> 00:15:00,143
Pei Xingjian,

190
00:15:00,143 --> 00:15:03,763
if you want to take this opportunity
to avenge Liuli,

191
00:15:03,763 --> 00:15:05,703
you've got the wrong idea,

192
00:15:05,703 --> 00:15:08,463
Let me tell you, even if my father agrees,

193
00:15:08,463 --> 00:15:10,083
neither my mother nor I will consent,

194
00:15:10,083 --> 00:15:13,243
Shanhu, what nonsense are you spouting?
Get back to your room quickly,

195
00:15:13,243 --> 00:15:15,343
I'm not talking nonsense,

196
00:15:15,343 --> 00:15:18,583
Father-in-law, I just spoke without thinking,

197
00:15:18,583 --> 00:15:21,463
Now, it's Shanhu who insists on
becoming a concubine,

198
00:15:21,463 --> 00:15:23,563
There's nothing that can be done about it,

199
00:15:24,963 --> 00:15:27,763
What's wrong with being a concubine?
Just like my mother,

200
00:15:27,763 --> 00:15:30,623
What does my mother lack
compared to the legitimate wife?

201
00:15:30,623 --> 00:15:33,503
Back then, didn't she
suppress the legitimate wife completely?

202
00:15:33,503 --> 00:15:36,243
You! Shanhu, don't embarrass yourself here,

203
00:15:36,243 --> 00:15:38,143
Stop talking nonsense and go back immediately!

204
00:15:38,143 --> 00:15:40,423
You have no say in this matter,

205
00:15:40,423 --> 00:15:44,763
Shanhu! Shanhu!

206
00:15:44,763 --> 00:15:46,303
Mother!

207
00:15:46,303 --> 00:15:48,583
Your grandfather thinks only of his own wealth,

208
00:15:48,583 --> 00:15:50,923
<i>[Obeying Moral Instruction is Intelligence]</i>
He cares nothing for our lives,

209
00:15:50,923 --> 00:15:53,143
It's not easy for you to have a chance
to make a giant leap forward,

210
00:15:53,143 --> 00:15:56,303
That will inevitably make some people jealous,

211
00:15:56,303 --> 00:16:00,043
How could she know? Even though a concubine
cannot overtake the legitimate wife's position,

212
00:16:00,043 --> 00:16:02,663
She can still make the legitimate wife
unable to lift her head up,

213
00:16:02,663 --> 00:16:04,763
Still talking nonsense!

214
00:16:04,763 --> 00:16:07,383
This sentence is even more difficult
for Pei to understand,

215
00:16:07,383 --> 00:16:09,903
Do you really think that marrying a concubine

216
00:16:09,903 --> 00:16:11,323
can wear down the legitimate wife?

217
00:16:11,323 --> 00:16:13,216
Exactly,

218
00:16:15,523 --> 00:16:18,303
You're about to marry into
the Hedong Duke's Residence as a concubine,

219
00:16:18,303 --> 00:16:20,843
About that deafeningly loud opinion just now,

220
00:16:20,843 --> 00:16:23,483
I think the Princess
and the Crown Prince's Wife

221
00:16:23,483 --> 00:16:25,183
will be very pleased to hear it,

222
00:16:25,183 --> 00:16:28,563
It would be good to be guarded
against it in the future,

223
00:16:31,403 --> 00:16:33,823
Liuli, let's go,

224
00:16:33,823 --> 00:16:37,083
You wronged me, How dare you
talk nonsense to Hedong Duke's family?

225
00:16:37,083 --> 00:16:40,523
For such a big matter, Pei indeed would not

226
00:16:41,163 --> 00:16:43,583
dare to hide anything from the elders,

227
00:16:44,643 --> 00:16:47,503
<i>[Obeying Moral Instruction is Intelligence]</i>
Shouyue, please stay for a moment,

228
00:16:47,503 --> 00:16:50,943
Shanhu is ignorant, and she only cares about
the pleasure of tongue-lashing,

229
00:16:50,943 --> 00:16:52,783
We can't take it seriously,

230
00:16:52,783 --> 00:16:56,443
Moreover, if this matter spreads out,

231
00:16:56,443 --> 00:17:02,023
I'm afraid it won't be too good
for Liuli's reputation either,

232
00:17:02,643 --> 00:17:05,043
Father, there's no need to worry about me,

233
00:17:05,043 --> 00:17:07,223
I'm married under a marriage contract,
openly and solemnly,

234
00:17:07,223 --> 00:17:10,503
As the legitimate wife,
after hearing what my younger sister just said,

235
00:17:10,503 --> 00:17:12,463
I also find it unbearable,

236
00:17:12,463 --> 00:17:14,723
Furthermore, if these words are spread out,

237
00:17:14,723 --> 00:17:16,903
it has nothing to do with me,
the legitimate wife,

